main event: A witness reported seeing an unidentified object cross over a field in Mascoutah, Illinois on March 22, 2022.
interesting points: The observation was visual and reported to be unusual without an explanation,The object did not remain in sight for long,It was not reported how long the observation lasted,There was no physical evidence or photographs related to the sighting,The source of the report is unknown.
witness description: Witness reported seeing an object crossing over a field.
